      • generateCRL

        public String generateCRL(User registrar,
                          Date revokedBefore,
                          Date revokedAfter,
                          Date expireBefore,
                          Date expireAfter)
                   throws InvalidArgumentException,
                          GenerateCRLException
        Generate certificate revocation list.
        Parameters:
        registrar - admin user configured in CA-server
        revokedBefore - Restrict certificates returned to revoked before this date if not null.
        revokedAfter - Restrict certificates returned to revoked after this date if not null.
        expireBefore - Restrict certificates returned to expired before this date if not null.
        expireAfter - Restrict certificates returned to expired after this date if not null.
        Throws:
        InvalidArgumentException
        GenerateCRLException
